* EasyBuild is a software build and installation framework that allows you to manage (scientific) software on High Performance Computing (HPC) systems in an efficient way.

- Easybuild website
 http://easybuilders.github.io/easybuild/
- Easybuild is developed on <a href="https://github.com/easybuilders/easybuild">GitHub</a> and has 377 stars
- Easybuild first developed in <a href="../lists/originCommunities.html#httpsGithubComEasybuilders">https://github.com/easybuilders/</a>
- file extensions for Easybuild include eb
